OL,3,CCould Labour's workers' rights
OL,4,Clegislation be diluted after Rayner's
OL,5,Cdeparture?
OL,7,FTrade unions are concerned Labour's
OL,8,Flandmark workers' rights legislation
OL,9,Fcould be watered down after the
OL,10,Fdeparture of Angela Rayner and the
OL,11,Fgovernment reshuffle.
OL,13,FThe plans are due to become law within
OL,14,Fweeks, but after some of the key
OL,15,Farchitects of the reforms left
OL,16,Fgovernment on Friday, unions are
OL,17,Furging the government not to back down
OL,18,Fin the face of pressure from
OL,19,Fbusinesses.
