OL,3,CCould Labour's workers' rights
OL,4,Clegislation be diluted after Rayner's
OL,5,Cdeparture?
OL,7,FThe key reforms in the bill include
OL,8,Fplans that give workers immediate
OL,9,Faccess to sick pay and parental leave,
OL,10,Fas well as bringing in a ban on some
OL,11,Fzero-hour contracts, and most fire and
OL,12,Frehire practices.
OL,14,FDespite previously promising to ban
OL,15,Fzero-hours contracts entirely before
OL,16,Fthe election, Labour watered down the
OL,17,Fpledge to add in the word
OL,18,F"exploitative", allowing some workers
OL,19,Fto opt to stay on zero-hours contracts.
