OL,3,CCould Labour's workers' rights
OL,4,Clegislation be diluted after Rayner's
OL,5,Cdeparture?
OL,7,FCurrently, workers must be off work
OL,8,Fsick for three days in a row to
OL,9,Fqualify for statutory sick pay.
OL,11,FThe bill will also ban most fire and
OL,12,Frehire practices, and double the
OL,13,Fpenalties on companies for using fire
OL,14,Fand rehire.
OL,16,FWorkers will also get a "day-one
OL,17,Fright" to claim unfair dismissal - a
OL,18,Fsignificant change from the current
OL,19,Ftwo-year qualifying period.
