OL,3,CCould Labour's workers' rights
OL,4,Clegislation be diluted after Rayner's
OL,5,Cdeparture?
OL,7,FBusiness groups have been urging the
OL,8,Fgovernment to reverse the plans,
OL,9,Fbecause they say they will "damage
OL,10,Fgrowth and employment, undermining the
OL,11,Fgovernment's own goals."
OL,13,FIn a letter earlier this year, key
OL,14,Fbusiness groups said the bill was a "a
OL,15,Frecipe for damaging, not raising,
OL,16,Fliving standards."
OL,18,FThe Conservatives have dubbed the
OL,19,Fplans a "union wish list" that will
OL,20,F"make the UK one of the worst places
OL,21,Fto hire."
