OL,7,FThe dramatic changes at the top of
OL,8,Fgovernment have sparked fear from the
OL,9,Funions that the government could water
OL,10,Fdown the bill, as part of their
OL,11,Fattempt to reset after a turbulent
OL,12,Fyear.
OL,14,FThe Sun newspaper also reported on
OL,15,FSunday that Sir Keir Starmer is facing
OL,16,Fpressure to dilute the bill,
OL,17,F"including within the Cabinet."
